-- Thomson won't comment on "rumors" of Reuters bid
-- 
-- Fri May 4, 2007 9:31am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/04/us-reuters-takeover-comment-idUSTOR00171220070504

 

 TORONTO  (Reuters) - Canadian electronic publisher Thomson Corp. TOC.TO TOC.N said on Friday it will not comment on media reports suggesting that the company is in talks to buy financial news and data group Reuters RTR.L. 

 "I will not comment on rumors and speculation", a spokesman said.